{
  "title": "Lab Overview",
  "uid": "lab-overview",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": { "from": "now-15m", "to": "now" },
  "tags": ["lab"],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "API request rate (by status)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (status) (rate(api_http_requests_total[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{status}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "API latency (p50 / p95 / p99)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le) (rate(api_http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p50"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(api_http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(api_http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "exemplar": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Queue depth (work queues)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rabbitmq_queue_messages{queue=~\".*-processing\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{queue}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Dead-letter queues",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rabbitmq_queue_messages{queue=~\".+\\\\.dlq\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{queue}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Worker throughput (success/s)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rate({__name__=~\".+_processing_success_total\"}[2m])",
          "legendFormat": "{{__name__}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Worker errors (errors/s)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 16 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rate({__name__=~\".+_processing_errors_total\"}[2m])",
          "legendFormat": "{{__name__}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Auth request rate",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 24 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(auth_service_http_requests_total[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "requests"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "GraphRAG processing",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 24 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rate(graphrag_messages_processed_total[2m])",
          "legendFormat": "processed/s ({{status}})"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "graphrag_currently_processing",
          "legendFormat": "in flight"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Traces (Tempo)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 32 },
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "traces",
      "title": "Recent traces",
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 33 },
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "queryType": "traceqlSearch",
          "filters": [],
          "limit": 20
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Trace workflow",
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 33 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Find a trace**\n\n- [Explore → Tempo](/explore?left=%7B%22datasource%22%3A%22tempo%22%2C%22queries%22%3A%5B%7B%22refId%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22queryType%22%3A%22traceqlSearch%22%7D%5D%7D) — TraceQL search across services.\n- The API latency panel carries **exemplars**: green dots on the p99 series deep-link into the exact trace.\n- Copy a `trace_id` into OpenSearch Discover (`lab-logs-*`, field `trace_id`) to see every log line of that request — the EXP-31 triage path."
      }
    }
  ]
}
